= Grab

Radiant CMS extension that provides an <r:grab url="http://some-url.com" /> tag to return some content (HTML) from somewhere.

This extension uses the hpricot gem, so make sure that's installed. 

= Usage

<r:grab url="http://som-url.com" [select="your xpath or css"] [class="your-class"] [id="your-id"] /> 

Built by smooshyLab http://www.smooshylab.com
